  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the efficacy of ultraviolet-A (UVA) and riboflavin application
      (also often referred to as corneal collagen crosslinking) as a method to enhance treatment of
      infectious keratitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
